 <i>scores the third goal.</i>

00:04:51.526 --> 00:04:54.128 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Despite the absence</i>
 <i>from Kojiro Hyuga,</i>

00:04:54.162 --> 00:04:55.495 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Toho Academy</i>
 <i>is still powerful.</i>

00:04:55.530 --> 00:04:57.265 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
 <i>What's wrong, Hyuga?</i>

00:04:57.297 --> 00:04:59.767 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>Why did you choose to stay</i>
 <i>in the sidelines?</i>

00:04:59.801 --> 00:05:00.968 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:05:01.002 --> 00:05:03.237 position:10% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Chubu is set
