00:05:03.271 --> 00:05:04.404 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>to redeem themselves.</i>

00:05:04.437 --> 00:05:05.840 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>It'll be a difficult task</i>

00:05:05.873 --> 00:05:08.375 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>with Wakashimazu</i>
 <i>covering the goal.</i>

00:05:08.408 --> 00:05:09.911 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>Toho Academy's goalkeeper</i>

