 <i>hasn't let a team score</i>
 <i>in the whole tournament.</i>

00:05:12.713 --> 00:05:15.315 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Toho's captain</i>
 <i>is determined.</i>

00:05:15.348 --> 00:05:17.450 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Ken]
 <i>They won't score.</i>

00:05:17.484 --> 00:05:19.987 position:19% line:11% align:start
[announcer] And there's
the crossover pass.

00:05:20.021 --> 00:05:21.656 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:05:21.689 --> 00:05:22.723 position:19% line:77% align:start
Impossible!

00:05:22.757 --> 00:05:23.624 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] But the ball
 <i>falls in the hands of</i>

00:05:23.658 --> 00:05:24.792 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>the goalie,</i>
 <i>Wakashimazu.</i>

00:05:24.826 --> 00:05:25.693 position:52% line:89% align:start
It can't be...

00:05:25.726 --> 00:05:27.261 position:30% line:83% align:start
That goalkeeper
is way too fast, guys.

00:05:27.295 --> 00:05:28.529 position:5% line:83% align:start
-[whistle]
-[cheering]

00:05:28.563 --> 00:05:30.463 position:16% line:11% align:start
[announcer] And the match
is over, everyone.

00:05:30.497 --> 00:05:32.332 position:21% line:83% align:start
The match has ended!
We did it!

00:05:32.365 --> 00:05:33.534 position:19% line:89% align:start
Toho is the best team.

00:05:33.568 --> 00:05:35.736 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Toho Academy
wins 3 to nothing

00:05:35.770 --> 00:05:37.572 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the goalkeeper</i>
 <i>Wakashimazu</i>

00:05:37.605 --> 00:05:39.472 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>remains as</i>
 <i>the best goalie</i>

00:05:39.507 --> 00:05:41.142 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>in the tournament.</i>

00:05:41.175 --> 00:05:43.144 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Well played, team!
-Good job, Ken!

00:05:43.177 --> 00:05:44.712 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well done, Takeshi!

00:05:44.745 --> 00:05:47.215 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll make it</i>
 <i>to the finals.</i>

00:05:47.248 --> 00:05:48.583 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Everyone from Toho</i>

00:05:48.616 --> 00:05:49.817 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>is giving everything</i>
-Yeah!

00:05:49.851 --> 00:05:51.853 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>they've got to compensate</i>
 <i>for Kojiro's</i>

00:05:51.886 --> 00:05:53.287 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>absence on the pitch.</i>
Yeah! [laugh]

00:05:53.321 --> 00:05:54.487 position:38% line:83% align:start
Woo-hoo!
We did it!

00:05:54.522 --> 00:05:56.557 position:21% line:11% align:start
[Tsubasa] If they're
this strong already,

00:05:56.591 --> 00:05:57.725 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I wouldn't want to know</i>
 <i>just how strong</i>

00:05:57.758 --> 00:05:59.126 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>they'll be with him</i>
 <i>on the pitch.</i>

00:06:01.128 --> 00:06:02.563 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>It'll be terrifying.</i>

00:06:06.033 --> 00:06:08.936 position:19% line:83% align:start
Okay, now it's our turn
to show them who we are!

00:06:08.970 --> 00:06:10.004 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:06:12.372 --> 00:06:14.308 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Machiko]
Matsuyama, wait up!

00:06:14.342 --> 00:06:15.710 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yeah?
What's going on?

00:06:17.545 --> 00:06:18.713 position:24% line:89% align:start
Go ahead, tell him.

00:06:21.115 --> 00:06:22.216 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is something wrong?

00:06:22.250 --> 00:06:23.450 position:24% line:83% align:start
You have something
to say to me?

00:06:25.086 --> 00:06:26.687 position:5% line:89% align:start
Tell him already, Yoshiko.

00:06:26.721 --> 00:06:27.822 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mhm...

00:06:27.855 --> 00:06:28.455 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:28.488 --> 00:06:29.590 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Koichi]
Captain!

00:06:29.624 --> 00:06:30.591 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:06:30.625 --> 00:06:33.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
We have to leave now.
They're waiting for us.

00:06:33.127 --> 00:06:34.461 position:35% line:83% align:start
Go ahead,
I'll catch up to you.

00:06:35.663 --> 00:06:37.098 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yoshiko, what's the matter
with you?

00:06:39.100 --> 00:06:40.268 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:06:40.301 --> 00:06:42.803 position:27% line:83% align:start
I just wanted to
wish you good luck, Captain.

00:06:42.837 --> 00:06:46.507 position:13% line:83% align:start
Thank you. Is that all...
you wanted to say to me?

00:06:47.909 --> 00:06:49.409 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:06:49.442 --> 00:06:51.579 position:13% line:89% align:start
I really appreciate that.

00:06:52.780 --> 00:06:53.814 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
 <i>What's up with her?</i>

00:06:53.848 --> 00:06:54.782 position:44% line:89% align:start
No!

00:06:54.815 --> 00:06:56.517 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
Okay, Furano, game on!

00:06:56.550 --> 00:06:57.818 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:06:57.852 --> 00:06:58.886 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[laugh]
-[sigh]

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.154 position:16% line:89% align:start
There's no helping you.

00:07:00.187 --> 00:07:01.355 position:30% line:83% align:start
We're gonna win
this one for sure!

00:07:01.389 --> 00:07:03.024 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Yoshiko] Yeah.
It's for the best.

00:07:03.057 --> 00:07:04.392 position:30% line:89% align:start
We can do it!

00:07:04.424 --> 00:07:05.626 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Let's go!
 <i>-[Yoshiko] I'm going to let</i>

00:07:05.660 --> 00:07:07.962 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>the captain focus on</i>
 <i>winning the match.</i>

00:07:07.995 --> 00:07:09.397 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>That's the only thing</i>
-Yeah! Come on, man!

00:07:09.429 --> 00:07:10.497 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>that matters right now.</i>
-I believe in us!

00:07:10.531 --> 00:07:11.732 position:30% line:89% align:start
We can do it!

00:07:11.766 --> 00:07:14.101 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:07:14.135 --> 00:07:15.403 position:16% line:89% align:start
Let's win this, Furano.

00:07:15.435 --> 00:07:17.138 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Let's win this, Furano.
-Let's win this, Furano.

