 <i>shouts their ceremonial</i>
 <i>war cry.</i>

00:07:24.178 --> 00:07:26.047 position:30% line:83% align:start
Go on, Furano!
Go on, Furano!

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:27.515 position:33% line:89% align:start
