00:07:31.786 --> 00:07:32.920 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>for the referee's</i>
 <i>whistle.</i>

00:07:32.954 --> 00:07:34.322 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tetsuo]
 <i>Perfect.</i>

00:07:34.355 --> 00:07:37.525 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll eliminate Team Furano</i>
 <i>to get to the semifinals,</i>

00:07:37.558 --> 00:07:39.660 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>and defeat Nankatsu.</i>

