[announcer] This is
 <i>the third match</i>

00:07:41.329 --> 00:07:42.830 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>of the quarterfinals.</i>

00:07:42.863 --> 00:07:44.665 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll see which of</i>
 <i>these teams</i>

00:07:44.699 --> 00:07:46.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>will make it to</i>
 <i>the top four.</i>

00:07:46.167 --> 00:07:47.068 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:07:47.101 --> 00:07:48.602 position:16% line:11% align:start
[announcer] The referee
blows his whistle

00:07:48.636 --> 00:07:50.438 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and Team Furano</i>
 <i>initiates the attack.</i>

00:07:50.470 --> 00:07:51.238 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Okay, Furano,
-[panting]

00:07:51.272 --> 00:07:52.440 position:5% line:89% align:start
let's go for a quick goal,

00:07:52.472 --> 00:07:53.407 position:33% line:83% align:start
-all right?
-Yeah!

00:07:53.441 --> 00:07:55.609 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm coming for you,
Matsuyama.

00:07:55.643 --> 00:07:57.345 position:10% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Minami-uwa's
 <i>captain</i>

00:07:57.378 --> 00:07:58.713 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>goes after Matsuyama.</i>

00:07:58.746 --> 00:07:59.814 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Looks like</i>
 <i>the captain's duel</i>

00:07:59.847 --> 00:08:01.282 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>will begin sooner</i>
 <i>than we thought.</i>

00:08:01.315 --> 00:08:02.883 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wakamatsu, you're open.

00:08:02.917 --> 00:08:04.318 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:08:04.352 --> 00:08:05.453 position:30% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:08:05.485 --> 00:08:06.587 position:30% line:83% align:start
Are you scared
to go up against me?

00:08:06.620 --> 00:08:09.023 position:13% line:83% align:start
Ha, I'm not afraid of you,
Ishida.

00:08:09.056 --> 00:08:12.093 position:10% line:83% align:start
By now, you should know that
soccer is a team sport.

00:08:12.126 --> 00:08:14.061 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh sure, make excuses.

00:08:14.095 --> 00:08:15.162 position:16% line:89% align:start
[grunt] You say you have

00:08:15.196 --> 00:08:16.864 position:44% line:83% align:start
faith
on your teammates,

00:08:16.897 --> 00:08:19.834 position:13% line:83% align:start
but really, I think you're
afraid of losing the ball

00:08:19.867 --> 00:08:21.335 position:19% line:83% align:start
-and being humiliated,
-[grunt]

00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:22.203 position:33% line:89% align:start
aren't you?

00:08:22.236 --> 00:08:23.070 position:16% line:89% align:start
[announcer] Minami-uwa

00:08:23.104 --> 00:08:24.638 position:24% line:89% align:start
intercepts the pass

00:08:24.672 --> 00:08:26.173 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>and now has the ball.</i>

00:08:26.207 --> 00:08:27.475 position:33% line:83% align:start
-The field!
-[gasp]

00:08:27.508 --> 00:08:30.044 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] The ball's
passed to Captain Ishida.

00:08:30.077 --> 00:08:31.078 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:08:31.112 --> 00:08:32.480 position:33% line:83% align:start
Here comes
the first goal.

00:08:32.513 --> 00:08:33.848 position:24% line:89% align:start
Quickly, go defend.

00:08:33.881 --> 00:08:36.617 position:24% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Ishida
demonstrates great technique

00:08:36.650 --> 00:08:38.652 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>and runs with great speed</i>
 <i>towards the goal.</i>

00:08:38.686 --> 00:08:40.521 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Furano's defense</i>
 <i>runs to cover him,</i>

00:08:40.554 --> 00:08:43.591 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>but Minami-uwa's captain</i>
 <i>isn't alone.</i>

00:08:43.624 --> 00:08:45.226 position:24% line:83% align:start
-I'm right behind.
-[grunt]

00:08:45.259 --> 00:08:45.960 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:08:45.993 --> 00:08:46.994 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:08:47.028 --> 00:08:48.496 position:33% line:11% align:start
 <i>[announcer] Ishida</i>
 <i>tricks the defense</i>

00:08:48.529 --> 00:08:49.897 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a fake pass.</i>

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:51.732 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Furano is</i>
 <i>completely fooled.</i>

00:08:51.766 --> 00:08:53.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
Don't underestimate us,
Ishida.

00:08:53.868 --> 00:08:54.969 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:08:55.002 --> 00:08:56.370 position:35% line:83% align:start
How slow.
[grunt]

00:08:56.404 --> 00:08:57.238 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Ishida kicks
 <i>the ball</i>

00:08:57.271 --> 00:08:58.507 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>with a crossover pass,</i>

00:08:58.539 --> 00:09:00.041 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>but it looks like</i>
 <i>it's too high up.</i>

00:09:00.074 --> 00:09:02.511 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's going straight</i>
 <i>into the goalie's hands.</i>

00:09:02.543 --> 00:09:04.111 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's no problem</i>
 <i>for the keeper, Kato.</i>

00:09:04.145 --> 00:09:05.146 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's mine.

00:09:05.179 --> 00:09:06.013 position:41% line:89% align:start
-What?

00:09:06.047 --> 00:09:07.516 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Now it's my turn.

00:09:07.548 --> 00:09:09.784 position:21% line:83% align:start
[announcer] But now,
Minami-uwa's forward, Takei,

00:09:09.817 --> 00:09:12.521 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>comes at full speed</i>
 <i>to reclaim the pass.</i>

00:09:12.553 --> 00:09:13.522 position:13% line:83% align:start
-That's it. You can do it,
-[gasp]

00:09:13.554 --> 00:09:14.355 position:41% line:89% align:start
Takei.

00:09:14.388 --> 00:09:15.689 position:27% line:83% align:start
I won't let you.
[yell]

00:09:15.723 --> 00:09:17.526 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Takei jumps
for a header.

00:09:17.558 --> 00:09:20.094 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>This will be</i>
 <i>a midair duel.</i>

00:09:20.127 --> 00:09:21.629 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:22.531 --> 00:09:23.964 position:21% line:77% align:start
-[gasp]
-[announcer]
Goal!

00:09:23.998 --> 00:09:26.500 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Minami-uwa</i>
 <i>scores the first goal</i>

00:09:26.535 --> 00:09:27.536 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>with a spectacular</i>
 <i>header.</i>

00:09:27.568 --> 00:09:28.402 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:28.436 --> 00:09:30.438 position:5% line:83% align:start
They just scored
on Furano.

00:09:30.471 --> 00:09:31.939 position:16% line:89% align:start
What a great job, Takei.

00:09:31.972 --> 00:09:33.674 position:13% line:83% align:start
It was an excellent pass,
Captain.

00:09:33.707 --> 00:09:36.043 position:16% line:89% align:start
I had no problem at all.

00:09:36.077 --> 00:09:37.812 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>This is incredible.</i>

00:09:37.845 --> 00:09:39.680 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>For the first time,</i>
 <i>we witness Team Furano</i>

00:09:39.713 --> 00:09:41.449 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>get scored on</i>
 <i>during the tournament.</i>

00:09:41.482 --> 00:09:42.416 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:42.450 --> 00:09:44.385 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, this can't be.

00:09:44.418 --> 00:09:45.554 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>Now Team Minami-uwa</i>

00:09:45.586 --> 00:09:47.421 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>is leading the match</i>
 <i>by a goal.</i>

00:09:47.455 --> 00:09:48.689 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>How will Team Furano</i>
 <i>respond</i>

00:09:48.722 --> 00:09:50.124 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>under this circumstance?</i>

00:09:50.157 --> 00:09:52.093 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Captain Matsuyama</i>
 <i>seems worried.</i>

00:09:52.126 --> 00:09:54.563 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Yoshiko]Please,
you have to win, Captain.

00:09:54.595 --> 00:09:56.063 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:09:57.331 --> 00:09:58.533 position:19% line:11% align:start
[announcer] And now,
Team Furano

00:09:58.567 --> 00:10:00.134 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>starts up the match.</i>

00:10:00.167 --> 00:10:01.168 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:01.202 --> 00:10:02.269 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's this?

00:10:02.303 --> 00:10:04.071 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[cheering]
-Yeah!

00:10:04.105 --> 00:10:05.306 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-All right!

00:10:05.339 --> 00:10:06.508 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's mine.

00:10:06.541 --> 00:10:07.842 position:10% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Minami-uwa
 <i>has the ball.</i>

00:10:07.875 --> 00:10:09.710 position:24% line:83% align:start
Great, let's score
the second goal.

00:10:09.743 --> 00:10:11.946 position:10% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Furano is
losing control of the match

00:10:11.979 --> 00:10:13.848 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>to a well organized</i>
 <i>Team Minami-uwa.</i>

00:10:13.881 --> 00:10:16.551 position:19% line:83% align:start
Everyone, remain calm.
Don't lose your cool.

00:10:16.585 --> 00:10:18.052 position:24% line:83% align:start
We've been through
worse times.

00:10:18.085 --> 00:10:18.986 position:24% line:89% align:start
Get the ball back.

00:10:19.019 --> 00:10:20.721 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Yes, Captain!
-Yes, Captain!

00:10:20.754 --> 00:10:21.856 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-It's mine!

00:10:21.889 --> 00:10:23.958 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Matsuyama
inspires his team

00:10:23.991 --> 00:10:24.758 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>not to give up</i>
 <i>and Team Furano is</i>

00:10:24.792 --> 00:10:26.595 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>able to recover the ball.</i>

00:10:26.627 --> 00:10:28.095 position:16% line:89% align:start
Here it comes, Captain.

00:10:28.129 --> 00:10:29.430 position:35% line:89% align:start
I got it!

00:10:29.463 --> 00:10:32.199 position:13% line:11% align:start
 <i>Team Minami-uwa is sure</i>
 <i>to think I'll pass the ball.</i>

00:10:32.233 --> 00:10:33.167 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>However, this time...</i>

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:34.435 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:10:34.468 --> 00:10:35.436 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:35.469 --> 00:10:36.571 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'll be attacking.</i>

00:10:36.605 --> 00:10:37.972 position:21% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Matsuyama
runs with the ball

00:10:38.005 --> 00:10:40.474 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and heads to</i>
 <i>the opponent's goal.</i>

00:10:40.509 --> 00:10:41.642 position:30% line:89% align:start
Dammit it all.

00:10:41.675 --> 00:10:43.010 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought he was going to
pass the ball.

00:10:43.043 --> 00:10:46.213 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Will Matsuyama
 <i>attempt to score a goal?</i>

00:10:46.247 --> 00:10:47.915 position:27% line:83% align:start
You're skilled,
Matsuyama,

00:10:47.948 --> 00:10:49.717 position:24% line:83% align:start
but you'll never be
better than I am.

00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:51.352 position:27% line:83% align:start
I won't let you
shoot the ball.

00:10:51.385 --> 00:10:52.621 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:52.653 --> 00:10:54.155 position:10% line:83% align:start
[annoucer] And Team Furano's
 <i>captain</i>

00:10:54.188 --> 00:10:56.223 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>makes a pass</i>
 <i>instead of shooting.</i>

00:10:56.257 --> 00:10:57.191 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's impossible.

00:10:57.224 --> 00:10:58.993 position:10% line:83% align:start
Kazumasa, you're all alone.
Score! Yeah!

00:10:59.026 --> 00:10:59.793 position:21% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Oda
 <i>is by himself</i>

00:10:59.827 --> 00:11:01.495 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>in front of the goal.</i>

00:11:01.530 --> 00:11:03.632 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, it's my chance.

00:11:03.664 --> 00:11:05.366 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[announcer] Oda takes the shot

00:11:05.399 --> 00:11:06.400 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>and...</i>

00:11:06.433 --> 00:11:08.736 position:7% line:83% align:start
-it goes above the goalpost.
-[gasp]

00:11:08.769 --> 00:11:10.371 position:27% line:83% align:start
-What bad luck!
-[gasp]

00:11:10.404 --> 00:11:12.373 position:38% line:83% align:start
Ugh...
This one was too close.

00:11:12.406 --> 00:11:13.741 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uhh...
-Real good attempt,

00:11:13.774 --> 00:11:15.376 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Kazumasa.
-It's no biggie.

00:11:15.409 --> 00:11:17.244 position:19% line:83% align:start
It'll go in next time,
Kazumasa.

00:11:17.278 --> 00:11:18.513 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry, Captain.

00:11:18.547 --> 00:11:19.780 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laugh]

00:11:19.813 --> 00:11:21.282 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're worse</i>
 <i>than I imagined.</i>

00:11:24.818 --> 00:11:26.921 position:33% line:83% align:start
Let's go for
our second goal.

00:11:26.954 --> 00:11:29.390 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Ishida kicks
a crossover pass.

00:11:29.423 --> 00:11:31.560 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>It might be</i>
 <i>the second goal.</i>

00:11:31.593 --> 00:11:33.294 position:27% line:83% align:start
We won't let you
underestimate...

00:11:33.327 --> 00:11:34.529 position:16% line:89% align:start
...Team Furano anymore.

00:11:34.563 --> 00:11:36.163 position:16% line:89% align:start
We're going to stop him.

00:11:36.197 --> 00:11:38.199 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:11:38.232 --> 00:11:41.402 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Furano's
defense intervenes.

00:11:41.435 --> 00:11:42.637 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:42.671 --> 00:11:43.804 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thanks so much, guys.

00:11:43.837 --> 00:11:46.173 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] The goalkeeper
has the ball.

00:11:46.207 --> 00:11:47.542 position:5% line:89% align:start
What're they doing?

00:11:47.576 --> 00:11:49.076 position:10% line:83% align:start
They're playing very weird,
aren't they.

00:11:49.109 --> 00:11:51.378 position:30% line:83% align:start
Team Furano's
only defending.

00:11:51.412 --> 00:11:53.113 position:16% line:89% align:start
Team Minami-uwa looks...

00:11:53.147 --> 00:11:56.283 position:21% line:83% align:start
to be way stronger
than we ever thought.

00:11:56.317 --> 00:11:57.586 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>That's right</i>

00:11:57.619 --> 00:11:59.453 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>We can't</i>
 <i>underestimate anyone.</i>

00:12:00.689 --> 00:12:01.755 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:02.990 --> 00:12:04.593 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Oh no!
-[whistle]

00:12:04.626 --> 00:12:05.926 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>And the referee signals</i>

00:12:05.960 --> 00:12:07.529 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>the end of</i>
 <i>the first half.</i>

00:12:07.562 --> 00:12:09.698 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] <i>What the</i>
 <i>hell are you doing?</i>

00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:10.998 position:5% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Team Furano
hasn't been able

00:12:11.031 --> 00:12:13.434 position:13% line:11% align:start
 <i>to tie the scoreboard</i>
 <i>during this first half.</i>

00:12:13.467 --> 00:12:14.603 position:52% line:83% align:start
Let's go, guys.

00:12:14.636 --> 00:12:15.570 position:24% line:83% align:start
We have to start
warming up for our match.

00:12:15.604 --> 00:12:16.403 position:35% line:89% align:start
Come on.

00:12:16.437 --> 00:12:17.171 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:12:17.204 --> 00:12:18.472 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm sure they'll
turn the tables

00:12:18.506 --> 00:12:20.007 position:24% line:83% align:start
on Team Minami-uwa
soon enough.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:22.943 position:10% line:83% align:start
Their team is much stronger
than I had imagined.

00:12:22.977 --> 00:12:23.712 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:12:23.744 --> 00:12:25.246 position:13% line:89% align:start
They have to do something,

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:27.414 position:24% line:83% align:start
if our team doesn't
win this match

00:12:27.448 --> 00:12:28.717 position:21% line:89% align:start
and gets eliminated,

00:12:28.749 --> 00:12:31.452 position:13% line:83% align:start
you'll have to say goodbye
to the captain today.

00:12:31.485 --> 00:12:32.687 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:12:32.721 --> 00:12:33.988 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Ms. Fujisawa]
 <i>Listen, Yoshiko...</i>

00:12:34.021 --> 00:12:35.856 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>your father's already</i>
 <i>waiting for us</i>

00:12:35.889 --> 00:12:37.858 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>in the United States.</i>

00:12:37.891 --> 00:12:39.326 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>But wait, Mother...</i>

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.629 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>You said we would stay</i>

00:12:40.662 --> 00:12:42.564 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>until the first semester</i>
 <i>was over.</i>

00:12:42.597 --> 00:12:43.998 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I know you've</i>
 <i>put a lot of effort</i>

00:12:44.031 --> 00:12:45.600 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>as your team's manager...</i>

00:12:45.634 --> 00:12:47.301 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>but we can't stay in Japan</i>
 <i>anymore.</i>

00:12:47.334 --> 00:12:49.604 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's a better life</i>
 <i>waiting for you elsewhere.</i>

00:12:49.638 --> 00:12:50.838 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I promise to go</i>

00:12:50.871 --> 00:12:52.773 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>once our team</i>
 <i>loses the tournament, Mom.</i>

00:12:52.806 --> 00:12:54.643 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Ms. Fujisawa] You sure?
You're okay with that?

00:12:54.676 --> 00:12:55.476 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Mhm.</i>

00:12:56.511 --> 00:12:57.978 position:16% line:89% align:start
You can do it, Captain.

00:13:01.081 --> 00:13:04.118 position:5% line:83% align:start
[narrator] We'll be right back
with Captain Tsubasa.

00:13:09.189 --> 00:13:10.291 position:35% line:83% align:start
